			<<else>>
				<span class="red"><<Hes>> ready for you.</span>
				<<set $huntGame.end to "ambushFailed">>
			<</if>>
			<<exit>>
		<<case "hideKeep">>
			<<if _forceConfrontation>>
				<span class="red"><<He>> suddenly turns to face you, and runs towards you!</span>
				<<set $huntGame.end to "caught">><<set $phase to "noDodge">>
				<<exit>>
			<<elseif $skulduggerysuccess>>
				After a moment of searching, <span class="green"><<he>> moves on. You stealthily follow.</span>
				<<if $huntGame.consensual and $huntGame.hunter is "other">>
					<br>
					<span class="gold">You are now the hunter.</span>
					<<set $huntGame.hunter to "player">>
				<</if>>
				<br><br>

				<span class="purple">The hunt intensifies...</span> <<note "+ Skulduggery Difficulty" "purple">>
				<<set $huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMin += 20>><<set $huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMax += 20>>
				<<set $huntGame.otherTracked to "trail">><<set $huntGame.distance to 2>>
			<<else>>
				<span class="red"><<He>> suddenly turns to face you, and runs towards you!</span>
				<<set $huntGame.end to "caught">><<set $phase to "noDodge">>
				<<exit>>
			<</if>>
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	/* Adversary actions */
	<<if !$huntGame.playerTracked and ($huntGame.hunter is "other" or $huntGame.distance gte 3)>>
		<<set $huntGame.otherAction to "track">>
		<<set $_otherTrackingDiff to currentSkillValue("skulduggery")>>
		<<if ["stealth", "hide"].includes($huntGame.playerAction) and $_actionPassed>>
			/* Failed to track */
		<<elseif $NPCList[0].skills.security gte random(1, $_otherTrackingDiff)>>
			<<set $huntGame.playerTracked to true>>
		<</if>>

		<<if ["hide"].includes($huntGame.playerAction) or $huntGame.playerAction is "stealth" and !$_actionPassed>>
			<<set $huntGame.distance-->>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $huntGame.hunter is "player">>
		<<if ["hide", "ambush"].includes($huntGame.otherAction) and !$huntGame.noMoreHiding>>
			<<set $huntGame.otherHideTimer-->>
			<<if random(0, 2)>>
				<<set $huntGame.otherAction to "ambush">>
			<</if>>
			<<if $huntGame.otherHideTimer lte 0>>
				<<set $huntGame.noMoreHiding to true>>
			<</if>>
		<<elseif $huntGame.distance gte 3 and random(0, 1) and !$huntGame.noMoreHiding>>
			<<set $huntGame.otherAction to "hide">>
			<<set $huntGame.otherHideTimer ||= 3>>
		<<elseif $huntGame.distance gte 2>>
			<<set $huntGame.otherAction to "stealth">>
			<<if $huntGame.playerTracked and !($huntGame.playerAction is "hunt" and $huntGame.otherTracked and $_actionPassed)>>
				<<set $huntGame.distance++>>
			<<elseif !$huntGame.playerTracked>>
				<<set $huntGame.distance += random(-1, 1)>>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<set $huntGame.otherAction to "run">>
			<<if $huntGame.playerTracked and !($huntGame.playerAction is "hunt" and $huntGame.otherTracked and $_actionPassed)>>
				<<set $huntGame.distance += 2>>
			<<elseif $huntGame.playerTracked>>
				<<set $huntGame.distance += 1>>
			<<else>>
				<<set $huntGame.distance += random(-1, 2)>>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $huntGame.playerTracked>>
		<<set $huntGame.otherAction to "hunt">>
		<<set $huntGame.distance-->>
	<<else>>
		<<set $huntGame.otherAction to "stealth">>
	<</if>>

	/* Give player information if tracked */
	<<if $huntGame.otherTracked>>
		<<if $huntGame.playerAction is "tracked" and $_actionPassed>>
			You spend some time following it, and realise that
			<<if $huntGame.otherAction is "track">>
				<<if $huntGame.playerTracked>>
					<<set $huntGame.hunterKnown to true>><<set $huntGame.playerTrackedKnown to true>>
					<<hes>> just tracked you too. <span class="pink">You're encircling each other.</span> It's cat and mouse, now.
				<<else>>
					<<set $huntGame.hunterKnown to true>>
					<<hes>> trying to track you too. <span class="green"><<He>> doesn't seem to know where you are yet!</span>
					<<if $huntGame.consensual and $huntGame.hunter is "other">>
						<br>
						<span class="gold">You are now the hunter.</span>
						<<set $huntGame.hunter to "player">>
					<</if>>
				<</if>>
			<<elseif $huntGame.otherAction is "stealth">>
				<<hes>> moving slowly and stealthily. Not stealthily enough, yet.
			<<elseif $huntGame.otherAction is "run">>
				<<hes>> running.
				<<if $huntGame.playerTracked>>
					<<He>> must know you have <<his>> trail.
				<<else>>
					Blindly. <<He>> doesn't know exactly where you are.
				<</if>>
			<<elseif $huntGame.otherAction is "hunt">>
				<<set $huntGame.hunterKnown to true>><<set $huntGame.playerTrackedKnown to true>>
				<<hes>> hunting you, too. <span class="pink">You're encircling each other.</span> It's cat and mouse, now.
			<<else>>
				<<hes>> likely hiding somewhere ahead.
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<if ["hide"].includes($huntGame.playerAction) and $huntGame.otherTracked>>
				<<set $huntGame.otherTracked to false>>
				<span class="red">You lose <<his>> trail.</span>
			<<else>>
				<<switch $huntGame.otherAction>>
					<<case "track">>
						You can tell <<hes>> trying to track you, too.
						<<if $huntGame.playerTracked>>
							<<set $huntGame.hunterKnown to true>><<set $huntGame.playerTrackedKnown to true>>
							<span class="pink">You're encircling each other.</span>
						<<else>>
							<<set $huntGame.hunterKnown to true>>
							<span class="green"><<He>> doesn't seem to know where you are yet!</span>
							<<if $huntGame.consensual and $huntGame.hunter is "other">>
								<br>
								<span class="gold">You are now the hunter.</span>
								<<set $huntGame.hunter to "player">>
							<</if>>
						<</if>>
					<<case "stealth">>
						You can tell <<hes>> moving slowly and methodically.
						<<if !($huntGame.playerAction is "track" and $_actionPassed)>>
							<<set $skulduggerydifficulty to random($huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMin, $huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMax)>>
							<<skulduggerycheck "silent">>
						<</if>>
						<<if $skulduggerysuccess>>
							<span class="green">You still have <<his>> trail for now.</span>
							<<set $huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMin += 20>><<set $huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMax += 20>>
						<<else>>
							<span class="red"><<Hes>> good. You lose <<his>> trail.</span>
							<<set $huntGame.otherTracked to false>>
						<</if>>
					<<case "run">>
						You can tell <<hes>> running away.
						<<if $huntGame.playerTracked>>
							<<He>> must know you have <<his>> trail.
						<<else>>
							Blindly. <<He>> doesn't know exactly where you are.
						<</if>>
					<<case "hunt">>
						<<set $huntGame.hunterKnown to true>><<set $huntGame.playerTrackedKnown to true>>
						<<His>> movements are aggressive. <<Hes>> hunting you down.
						<<if $huntGame.hunter is "player">>
							<br>
							<span class="red">You are no longer the hunter.</span>
							<<set $huntGame.hunter to "other">>
						<</if>>
					<<default>>
						You can tell <<hes>> hiding somewhere.
						<<if !($huntGame.playerAction is "track" and $_actionPassed)>>
							<<set $skulduggerydifficulty to random($huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMin, $huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMax)>>
							<<skulduggerycheck "silent">>
						<</if>>
						<<if $skulduggerysuccess>>
							<span class="green">You still have <<his>> trail for now.</span>
							<<set $huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMin += 20>><<set $huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMax += 20>>
						<<else>>
							<span class="red"><<Hes>> good. You lose <<his>> trail.</span>
							<<set $huntGame.otherTracked to false>>
						<</if>>
				<</switch>>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</if>>

	/* Confrontation */
	<<if $huntGame.distance lte 1 and $huntGame.playerAction isnot "hide" or _forceConfrontation>>
		<<if ["hide","ambush"].includes($huntGame.otherAction) and $huntGame.hunter is "player" and $huntGame.playerAction is "stealth" and $_actionPassed and !_forceConfrontation>>
			<<set $huntGame.end to "chase">><<set $huntGame.chaseDistance to 1>>
			You spot <<= $huntGame.adversaryText>> hiding in the underbrush ahead! <span class="green">Thanks to your stealthy movement, you've spotted <<him>> first.</span>
			<br><br>

			You get the drop on <<him>>. <<He>> starts to run, but you're already right behind <<him>>.
		<<elseif $huntGame.otherAction is "ambush" or _forceConfrontation>>
			<<set $huntGame.end to "caught">>
			You hear a rustle from the bushes. <<He>> was waiting in ambush for you!
			<<if $huntGame.hunterKnown>>
				<br>
				<span class="red">You are no longer the hunter.</span>
			<</if>>
			<<set $huntGame.hunter to "other">>
			<<set $huntGame.playerTracked to true>>
		<<elseif $huntGame.hunter is "player">>
			<<set $huntGame.end to "chase">>
			You spot <<him>> skulking through the underbrush ahead. <<He>> sees you too. <<He>> starts running!
		<<else>>
			<<set $huntGame.end to "caught">>
			You hear running close by. <<Hes>> found you!
		<</if>>
		<<exit>>
	<</if>>

	<<set $huntGame.turn++>>
	<<if $huntGame.hunter is "player">>
		<<set $huntGame.playerHuntTimer ||= 7>>
		<<set $huntGame.playerHuntTimer-->>
		<<if !$huntGame.playerHuntTimer or _forceConfrontation>>
			<<if $huntGame.hunterKnown>>
				Something changes on the wind. You suddenly feel vulnerable.
				<br>
				<span class="red">You are no longer the hunter.</span>
				<br><br>
			<</if>>
			<<set $huntGame.hunter to "other">>
			<<set $huntGame.playerTracked to true>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<set $huntGame.distance to Math.clamp($huntGame.distance, 0, 7)>>
	<<set $huntGame.playerActionLast to $huntGame.playerAction>>
	<<pass 2>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanHuntOptions">>
	<<set $skulduggerydifficulty to random($huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMin, $huntGame.skills.skulduggeryMax)>>
	<<if $huntGame.distance lte 1 and $huntGame.playerAction is "hide">>
		You peek out from your hiding spot and see <<him>> searching for you. <span class="green"><<He>> hasn't seen you yet.</span>
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Ambush|$huntGame.event]]>><<set $huntGame.playerAction to "ambush">><<transform fox 1>><</link>><<physiquedifficulty 4000 17000>>
		<br>
		<<if $huntGame.consensual>>
			<<link [[Keep hiding, and track <<him>> once <<he>> leaves|$huntGame.event]]>><<set $huntGame.playerAction to "hideKeep">><</link>><<skulduggerydifficulty>>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Keep hiding, and escape once <<he>> leaves|$huntGame.event]]>><<set $huntGame.playerAction to "hideKeepEscape">><</link>><<skulduggerydifficulty>>
		<</if>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<if $huntGame.otherTracked>>
			<<if $huntGame.hunterKnown and $huntGame.hunter is "other">>
				<<link [[Force a confrontation|$huntGame.event]]>><<set $huntGame.playerAction to "hunt">><</link>><<note "- - Distance" "teal">>
			<<else>>
				<<link [[Hunt <<= $huntGame.adversaryText>> down|$huntGame.event]]>><<set $huntGame.playerAction to "hunt">><</link>><<note "- Distance" "teal">>
				<<if $huntGame.otherTracked and $huntGame.otherAction is "run">><<athleticsdifficulty $huntGame.skills.athleticsMin $huntGame.skills.athleticsMax>><</if>>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Track <<= $huntGame.adversaryText>>|$huntGame.event]]>><<set $huntGame.playerAction to "track">><</link>><<skulduggerydifficulty>>
		<</if>>
		<br>
		<<if $huntGame.hunterKnown and $huntGame.hunter is "other" and $huntGame.otherTracked and $huntGame.playerTracked and $huntGame.playerTrackedKnown>>
			<<link [[Move stealthily, and try to make <<= $huntGame.adversaryText>> lose your trail|$huntGame.event]]>><<set $huntGame.playerAction to "stealth">><</link>><<skulduggerydifficulty>>
			<br>
		<<elseif $huntGame.hunterKnown and $huntGame.hunter is "other" and $huntGame.otherTracked>>
			<<link [[Move stealthily away from <<= $huntGame.adversaryText>>|$huntGame.event]]>><<set $huntGame.playerAction to "stealth">><</link>><<skulduggerydifficulty>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Move stealthily|$huntGame.event]]>><<set $huntGame.playerAction to "stealth">><</link>><<skulduggerydifficulty>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
		<<link [[Hide|$huntGame.event]]>><<set $huntGame.playerAction to "hide">><</link>><<skulduggerydifficulty>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanCombatInit">>
	<<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
	<<set $enemyarousalmax to 1200>>
	<<set $enemyarousal += C.npc.Gwylan.lust>>
	<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("heat")>>
		<<set $enemyarousal += 100>>
	<</if>>
	<<set $combat_player_orgasm_target to Math.clamp(Math.ceil((C.npc.Gwylan.lust + C.npc.Gwylan.dom) / 100) + _gwylanStatus.count("heat"), 1, 10)>>
	<<if $arousal gte ($arousalmax / 5) * 4 and $combat_player_orgasm_target lte 1>>
		<<set $combat_player_orgasm_target++>>
	<</if>>
	<<if !_gwylanStatus.includes("wantsPregnancy")>>
		<<set $disableNormalImpregnation to true>>
		<<set $disableImpregnation to true>>
	<</if>>

	/* ToDo: Gwylan - delete when pregnancy is to be enabled */
	<<set $disableNormalImpregnation to true>>
	<<set $disableImpregnation to true>>

	/* ToDo: Gwylan - Start combat effects from hypnosis traits or bad end triggers? */
	<<set $_hypnoMessages to []>>
	<<if $gwylan.silence>>
		<<set $combat_silenced to true>>
		<<set $_hypnoMessages.push("<span class='red'>Gwylan steals your voice</span>")>>
	<</if>>
	<<if $gwylan.trance>>
		<<set $trance to 1>><<set $timer to $hypnosis_traits.devotion>>
		<<set $_hypnoMessages.push("<span class='lewd'>You are entranced</span>")>>
	<</if>>
	<<if $_hypnoMessages.length>>
		<<hypnosisText "<<= formatList($_hypnoMessages, '', true, '. ')>>.">>
		<br><br>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanNobody">>
	<<set $_banishedDays to _args[0] || 9>>
	<<if $gwylan.timer and ["active", "scorned"].includes(C.npc.Gwylan.state) and typeof $_banishedDays is "number">>
		<<set $gwylan.timer.nobody to new DateTime(Time.date).addDays($_banishedDays).timeStamp>>
		<<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar">>
			<<set $worn.neck.type.delete("leash")>>
			<<set $worn.neck.cursed to 0>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanDesc">><<silently>>
	<<if $forest_shop_intro or $gwylan_rescue or $gwylan_cafe_intro>>
		<<set _text_output to "Gwylan">>
	<<elseif _args.includes("the")>>
		<<set _text_output to "the mousy <<nnpc_gendery 'Gwylan'>>">>
	<<else>>
		<<set _text_output to "a mousy <<nnpc_gendery 'Gwylan'>>">>
	<</if>>
	<<if _args.includes("cap")>><<set _text_output to _text_output.toUpperFirst()>><</if>>
<</silently>><<print _text_output>><</widget>>

<<widget "shopkeeperDesc">><<silently>>
	<<if $forest_shop_intro or $gwylan_rescue or $gwylan_cafe_intro>>
		<<set _text_output to "shopkeeper">>
	<<else>>
		<<set _text_output to "<<nnpc_gendery 'Gwylan'>>">>
	<</if>>
	<<if _args.includes("cap")>><<capitalise>><</if>>
<</silently>><<print _text_output>><</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanRescueStats">>
	<<if !$gwylanRescue>>
		<<set $gwylanRescue to {
			seen: [],
			failed: "",
			count: 0,
			eden: 0,
		}>>
	<</if>>

	<<if !$gwylanRescue.seen.includes(_args[1])>>
		<<set _gwylanFirstRescue to _args[1]>>
	<</if>>

	<<if _args[0] is true>>
		<<set $rescued++>>
		<<set $gwylanRescue.count++>>
		<<if _args[2] is "Eden" and !$edenCagedEscape>>
			<<set $gwylanRescue.eden++>>
		<</if>>
		<<set $gwylanRescue.seen.pushUnique(_args[1])>>
	<<else>>
		<<set $gwylanRescue.failed to _args[1]>>
		<<set $gwylanRescue.seen.pushUnique(_args[1] + "Failed")>>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanReunion">>
	당신은 <<badEndProse $badEndStats.last()?.source "at">>에서 보낸 시간에 대해 그에게 이야기한다. 그는 당신의 머리카락을 쓸어내리며 말없이 듣는다. 이야기를 마치자, 그는 당신의 이마에 키스한다.
	<<switch $badEndStats.last()?.source>>
		<<case "Underground Farm">>
			<<if $brownFoxRevealed>>
				"You're lucky to have gotten away from the High Elk. <<nnpc_Hes "Remy">> a powerful <<nnpc_gender "Remy">>, especially alongside <<nnpc_his "Remy">> Cannibal Fox."
			<<else>>
				"You're lucky to have gotten away from Remy. <<nnpc_Hes "Remy">> a powerful <<nnpc_gender "Remy">>."
			<</if>>
			<<He>> holds your cheeks between <<his>> palms, looking into your eyes.
			<<if $dissociation gte 1>>
				"They've stolen the light from your eyes." <<He>> hugs you again, tighter now.
			<<else>>
				"Remember that you're still human. Nothing they do will change that." <<He>> hugs you again, tighter now.
			<</if>>
			<<if !$gwylanTalked.includes("underground_farm")>>
				<<set _badEndFollowup to true>>
			<</if>>
		<<case "Wolf Cave">>
			"The wolves are usually so docile, but the black one has been growing more and more bold," <<he>> says. "I'm so sorry that <<if ($settings.monsterChance gte random(1, 100) and ($hallucinations gte 1 or !$settings.monsterHallucinationsOnly)) or $blackwolfmonster is 2>><<nnpc_he "Black Wolf">><<else>>it<</if>> put you through that."
			<<if !$gwylanTalked.includes("loincloth")>>
				<<set _badEndFollowup to true>>
			<</if>>
		<<case "Eden">>
			"The forest knows," <<he>> says. "All <<nnpc_he "Eden">> does is take and destroy." <<His>> eyes darken.
			<<if !$gwylanTalked.includes("loincloth")>>
				<<set _badEndFollowup to true>>
			<</if>>
		<<case "Underground Dungeon">>
			"That's absolutely horrid. People trafficked like objects to be used and discarded, it makes me sick imagining how many weren't so lucky to escape." <<He>> hugs you tighter. "I'm ever grateful you did."
			<<if !$gwylanTalked.includes("underground_brothel")>>
				<<set _badEndFollowup to true>>
			<</if>>
		<<case "Mines">>
			"I can't believe something so sinister is going on right beneath our feet," <<he>> says. "You're very strong for making it out."
		<<case "Asylum">>
			"One can find <<pherself>> going mad from such treatment," <<he>> says. "<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("hypnosis_removal")>>Remember, if<<else>>If<</if>> that <<nnpc_gender "Harper">> has made you think something that you would never normally think, <span class="blue">please come see me at the shop</span>. I can help."
			<<if !$gwylanTalked.includes("asylum")>>
				<<set _badEndFollowup to true>>
			<</if>>
		<<case "Prison">>
			"We all have to reap what we sow," <<he>> says, "but sometimes the punishment does not fit the crime.
			<<if $badEndStats.find(stat => stat.source === "Prison").reasonEnd is "prisonServed">>
				I'm glad you were able to withstand your sentence's length without withering."
			<<else>>
				I'm glad you were resourceful enough to escape."
			<</if>>
			<<if !$gwylanTalked.includes("prison")>>
				<<set _badEndFollowup to true>>
			<</if>>
		<<case "Pound">>
			<<if isLoveInterest("Gwylan")>>"<span class="lewd">I'm the only one who can treat you like that.</span>"<<else>>"It's beyond cruel to turn a human into an animal. I hope you remember who you are."<</if>>
		<<case "Kylar Abduction">>
			"네 친구?" 그는 놀라지 않은 것 같다. "그를 그런 극단적인 행동으로 몰아간 것이 무엇이었든 간에, 그건 너희 둘 모두에게 견디기 힘든 일이었을 거야."
			<br><br>

			<<if $syndromekylar is 1>>
				<<if !$gwylanTalked.includes("vampire")>>
					<<set _badEndFollowup to true>>
				<</if>>
				"그랬었죠. 하지만 그를 이해해요," 당신은 말한다. "그는 오해받고 있어요. 곁에 있어줄 사람이 필요할 뿐인데.
			<<else>>
				"그랬었죠," 당신은 말한다. "그를 이해할 수가 없어요.
			<</if>>
			그냥, 그 일이 끝나서 다행이라고 생각해요."
			<br><br>

			"I am, too," <<he>> says. <<if isLoveInterest("Gwylan")>>"I missed you."<</if>>
		<<case "Pirate Ship">>
			"That sounds... familiar," <<he>> says. "It sounds like quite an adventure. A heart at sea... I hope you didn't become lost in its depths."
		<<default>>
			Gwylan sticks a pinky in <<his>> ear. "What was that? Sorry, <span class="red">I think there's a bug here</span>. Go tell <span class="gold">PurityGuy</span> what you've been up to, not me."
	<</switch>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "schoolWalkChat">>
	<<set _gwylan to statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _robin to statusCheck("Robin")>>
	<<set _gwylanPresent to _args.includes("gwylan")>><<set _robinPresent to _args.includes("robin")>>
	<<cleareventpool>>

	<<if _gwylanPresent>>
		<<if !$weekly.gwylan_school_talk_classes>>
			<<addinlineevent "school_gwylan_classes" 1>>
				<<set $weekly.gwylan_school_talk_classes to 1>>
				<<if _robinPresent>>
					"How are classes going for you?" Gwylan asks.
				<<else>>
					"How are classes going for you?" <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> asks.
				<</if>>
				<<if $sciencetrait + $mathstrait + $englishtrait + $historytrait gte 16>>
					You proudly tell <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">> how you've aced every single one. <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> listens as you talk at length about the interesting facts you've learned.
					<br><br>

					"That's wonderful news, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>." <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> smiles. "Knowledge nourishes the brain. I hope you never stop trying to learn."
				<<elseif $sciencetrait + $mathstrait + $englishtrait + $historytrait gte 8 and ($sciencetrait lte 1 or $mathstrait lte 1 or $englishtrait lte 1 or $historytrait lte 1)>>
					<<set _badClass to $sciencetrait lte 1 ? "science" : $mathstrait lte 1 ? "maths" : $englishtrait lte 1 ? "English" : "history">>
					You tell <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">> they're are going well for the most part, but you're falling behind on _badClass.
					<br><br>

					<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> pats your head. "Everyone has their shortcomings. It's natural, so don't beat yourself up over it. Just do your best, okay?"
				<<elseif $sciencetrait + $mathstrait + $englishtrait + $historytrait gte 8>>
					You tell <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">> you're making good headway,
					<<if $stress gte ($stressmax / 5) * 3>>
						but that you're feeling stressed about all the school work.
						<br><br>

						Gwylan leans in and hugs you<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>, planting a kiss on your cheek. <<stress -10>><<llstress>><<else>>. <<stress -5>><<lstress>><</if>>
						<br><br>

						"I'm sorry to hear that. The school system can be very heartless when it comes to students' mental health. Don't let them whittle you down, you deserve a break."
					<<else>>
						and continuing to improve.
						<br><br>

						<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> smiles. "Good work, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>. It's always a wonder to learn more about this world we live in."
					<</if>>
				<<elseif $sciencetrait + $mathstrait + $englishtrait + $historytrait gte 4>>
					You tell <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">> it's going okay, nothing remarkable.
					<br><br>

					Gwylan shrugs. "I wouldn't say that. You're learning something new each day, no matter how small. That's good."
				<<elseif $sciencetrait + $mathstrait + $englishtrait + $historytrait is 0>>
					You grit your teeth. You know all your grades are awful. You try not to look at <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">> as you tell <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">> about your failures.
					<br><br>

					Gwylan frowns. "You're too hard on yourself. As long as you're trying, you're doing just fine, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>."
				<<else>>
					<<set _goodClass to []>>
					<<if $sciencetrait gte 1>><<set _goodClass.push("science")>><</if>>
					<<if $mathstrait gte 1>><<set _goodClass.push("maths")>><</if>>
					<<if $englishtrait gte 1>><<set _goodClass.push("English")>><</if>>
					<<if $historytrait gte 1>><<set _goodClass.push("history")>><</if>>
					You tell <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">> about your forward strides in _goodClass.pluck().
					<br><br>

					"Nice work. That's a difficult subject to grasp, so I'm proud of you for taking on the challenge!"
				<</if>>
				<br><br>
			<</addinlineevent>>
		<</if>>

		<<if Weather.precipitation is "rain">>
			<<addinlineevent "school_gwylan_rain" 1>>
				As you pass by a deep puddle, you're suddenly met with a big splash. <<lowerwet 100>><<underlowerwet 50>><<effectswater "water">><<exposure>> You look back to see Gwylan standing in the middle of it, jumping up and down without a care.
				<br><br>

				<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> stops, looks up at you
				<<if $exposed gte 1>>
					drenched from the waist down, and covers <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> mouth. "Oops," <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> says, <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> tone of voice betraying any attempt to appear surprised.
				<<else>>
					and smiles. "Sorry, I couldn't help it. That puddle was massive! Did you see the wave it made?" You can't help but agree.
				<</if>>
				<br><br>

				<<if hasSexStat("exhibitionism", 4) and $exposed is 1 and $uncomfortable.underwear is false or hasSexStat("exhibitionism", 5) and $exposed is 2 and $uncomfortable.nude is false>>
					<<if $worn.feet.type.includes("rugged")>>
						You smirk. Gwylan's not getting away with this. You get a running start, and jump straight towards <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">>. You manage to glimpse a brief moment of fear in <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> eyes when <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> realises what you're doing.
						<br><br>

						<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> yelps as your feet come crashing down into the puddle, completely drenching <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">> in water too. You grin smugly. "Oops."
						<br><br>

						<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> shakes some water off <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> <<npcClothesText _gwylan "lower">> and pouts, but you clearly see <<nnpc_hes "Gwylan">> enjoying it too. "I guess I should've expected that. Now we're both wet." <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> looks around and says "Come, we need to get dried off," taking your hand and running down the nearby alley, away from the rain. <<takeHandholdingVirginity "Gwylan" `(V.gwylanSeen.includes("partners") ? "romantic" : "consensual")`>>
						<br><br>

						You both spend a few minutes drying off before moving on. <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> winks at you mischievously as you exit the alley.
					<<else>>
						You take the opportunity to strike a few lewd poses for anybody watching. Gwylan giggles.
						<br><br>

						"<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "naughty">>. Come on, let's go get you dried off already." <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> takes your hand and leads you down an alley, away from the rain. <<takeHandholdingVirginity "Gwylan" `(V.gwylanSeen.includes("partners") ? "romantic" : "consensual")`>>
						<br><br>

						You spend a few minutes drying off before moving on.
					<</if>>
					<<fame 1 "exhibitionism">>
				<<elseif $exposed gte 1>>
					You instinctively <<if ["naked", "bellyShow"].includes($worn.upper.type)>>pull your $worn.upper.name down to <</if>>try to conceal your <<exposedlower>>.
					<br><br>

					"Aww, I'm sorry, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>. Here, let's go get you dried off. Follow me." <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> takes your hand and uses <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> body to cover you as <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> leads you down an alley, away from the rain. <<takeHandholdingVirginity "Gwylan" `(V.gwylanSeen.includes("partners") ? "romantic" : "consensual")`>>
					<br><br>

					You spend a few minutes drying off before moving on.
				<</if>>
				<br><br>
				<<dry_full>>
			<</addinlineevent>>
		<</if>>

		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>>
			<<addinlineevent "school_gwylan_handholding" 1>>
				You walk in silence for a while, when you feel Gwylan's hand brush up against yours. <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> takes it absentmindedly, before realising what <<nnpc_hes "Gwylan">> doing. <<takeHandholdingVirginity "Gwylan" `(V.gwylanSeen.includes("partners") ? "romantic" : "consensual")`>>
				<br><br>

				<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
					<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> suddenly grips your hand tighter, <span class="lewd">and kisses you on the cheek</span>. <<arousal 400>><<garousal>>
				<<else>>
					<<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> blushes, <span class="blue">and lets go</span>.
				<</if>>
				<br><br>
			<</addinlineevent>>
		<</if>>

		<<addinlineevent "school_gwylan_object" 1>>
			Gwylan gets your attention and points at
			<<print either(
				"a pretty rock.",
				"a piece of graffiti on the wall.",
				"a seagull swallowing a cigarette.",
				"a weird-looking house.",
				"a strangely shaped cloud.",
				"a kid with a fox beanie.",
				"a kid with a balloon.",
				"a street performer.",
				"a sign with a typo.",
				"a funny street name.",
				"a tired-looking teen.",
				"a family having a picnic.",
				"a funny licence plate.",
				"a police officer on a horse.",
				"a passing police car.",
				"a passing fire engine.",
				"a passing ambulance.",
				"a group of kids chasing after soap bubbles.",
				"some students chatting loudly.",
				"some kids playing on a slide.",
				"some people flying kites.",
				"someone dressed very extravagantly.",
				"someone getting splashed with a water balloon.",
				"someone shouting angrily into a phone.",
				"someone biking around with almost no clothes on.",
				"someone with very thick eyebrows.",
				"someone with enormous... assets.",
				"someone slapping a catcaller.",
				"someone in a rush dropping a stack of papers.",
				"someone struggling to eat a very thick sandwich.",
				"two shop owners arguing.",
				"two people arguing in a foreign language.",
				"two people stumbling out of a bar together.",
				"two birds fighting over a worm.",
				"two people sharing a large pizza.",
				"two people playfully fighting with sticks.",
				"three kids playing tag.",
				"three dogs jumping around and playing together."
			)>>
			<br><br>

			You spend some time chatting about it.
			<<if $rng gte 96>>
				You get really into the discussion, creating an elaborate but silly story from it. Gwylan laughs. <<stress -8>><<trauma -2>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><<llstress>><<ltrauma>><<gyearning>>
			<<else>>
				<<stress -4>><<lstress>>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>
		<</addinlineevent>>
	<</if>>

	<<addinlineevent "school_talk_nothing" 1>>
		/* Nothing */
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<runeventpool>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "witch">>
	<<if C.npc.Gwylan.pronoun is "m">>
		<<set _text_output to "witch">>
	<<else>>
		<<set _text_output to "witch">>
	<</if>>

	<<exit _text_output>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanRobin">>
	<<set $_incr to _args[0] or 1>>
	<<set $_cap to _args[1] or 0>>
	/* Note: $_cap could be used to add automatic breakpoints based on `$gwylanSeen` properties. For now, they're done manually with argument */

	<<if !$_cap or $gwylan.robin + $_incr lte $_cap>>
		<<set $gwylan.robin += $_incr>>
	<<elseif $gwylan.robin lt $_cap and $gwylan.robin + $_incr gte $_cap>>
		<<set $gwylan.robin to $_cap>>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "measuringcharmsimage">>
	<<set _softCorruption to Math.clamp(Math.ceil($world_corruption_soft / 10), 0, 10)>>
	<<set _hardCorruption to Math.clamp($world_corruption_hard, 0, 10)>>
	<<if $options.images is 1>>
		<div id="divcharms">
			<<if $world_corruption_soft gt 0 and $world_corruption_soft lt 10>>
				<img id="map" src="img/misc/prop/charm_big_0b.png">
			<<else>>
				<img id="map" @src="'img/misc/prop/charm_big_' + Math.clamp(Math.ceil($world_corruption_soft / 10), 0, 10) + '.png'">
			<</if>>
			<img id="maparrow" @src="'img/misc/prop/charm_small_' + Math.clamp($world_corruption_hard, 0, 10) + '.png'">
		</div>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanClothesValentinesContents">>

<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance")>>
	"I'll confess, Valentine's was my least favourite time of the year. You know how hesitant I was to be romantic with you. Once it starts, it all comes out like a flood."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> stops walking, and picks up one of the roses. A pink one. "It's not enough to be close. It's the gnawing, all-consuming yearning to be with the one you love. It's the dread of losing them.
	It's the fear of the future, tempered by the joy of the present. It's stopping to smell the roses, even when love hurts, and true love truly hurts."
	<<He>> tucks <<his>> head into the crook of your neck.
	<br><br>

	<<if isLoveInterest("Gwylan")>>
		"It was too much for me. I'm sorry I pushed you away, but I'm happy you're here with me now."
	<<else>>
		"You best remember your promise, dearest."
	<</if>>
	<<He>> continues thumbing the petals of the rose off to the side.
<<elseif $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning") or $gwylanSeen.includesAll("ritual_sex", "pink_rose")>>Gwylan lends a patient ear through it all, before speaking up <<himself>>.
	"I'll confess, Valentine's is my least favourite time of the year. I'm not terribly romantic." <<He>> pauses. "I try not to be, at least. Too many complicated emotions." <<His>> eyes seem to sharpen towards you at the word 'complicated'.
	"It's not all terrible, but in the long term, it's going to hurt. Infatuation is doomed to end in tragedy. Love hurts, and true love truly hurts."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> stops walking, and picks up one of the roses. A pink one. "Especially in a town like this. It looks so pretty from the outside, despite the thorns. But a careless grasp will leave your hands bloody all the same."
	<<His>> hand tenses up. <<He>> looks as though <<hes>> about to crush the head of the rose, but stops <<himself>>.
	<br><br>

	"Someone will always end up hurt, and carry that pain with them forever." <<He>> closes <<his>> eyes and places the rose back. "Is the joy worth the pain? Can one bear those memories for a lifetime?"
<<else>>
	"I'll confess, Valentine's is my least favourite time of the year. I'm not terribly romantic."
	<<He>> stops walking, and picks up one of the roses. A pink one.
	<br><br>

	"It looks so pretty from the outside. The petals of infatuation appear comforting. Like you could wrap yourself in them and take shelter, alongside someone who can keep you... warm."
	<<His>> expression is hollow, <<his>> eyes unfocused. With two fingers, <<he>> snaps the head of the rose clean off.
	<br><br>

	"It's doomed to end in tragedy, in a town like this. Those feelings, that person, will fade away, and leave something ugly behind. Love hurts, and true love truly hurts."
	<<He>> crushes the head of the rose in <<his>> hand, and blows the ruined petals away. They're caught by a phantom breeze. After a moment of dancing through the air, they escape through a nearby window with unsettling precision.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<link [[Say nothing|Gwylan Talk Clothes Valentines Silent]]>><</link>>
<br>
<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("romance")>>
	<<if !_hasLI>>
		<<link [[Agree with <<him>>|Gwylan Talk Clothes Valentines Agree]]>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includesAny("yearning", "pink_rose") and _hasLI>>
		<<link [[Tell <<him>> that <<hes>> wrong|Gwylan Talk Clothes Valentines Wrong]]>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 5>><</link>><<ggyearning>>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[Ask <<him>> where that came from|Gwylan Talk Clothes Valentines Ask]]>><</link>>
	<</if>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<link [[Hug <<him>>|Gwylan Talk Clothes Valentines Hug]]>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 2>><</link>><<gyearning>>
<br>
<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
	<<link [[Tell <<him>> that you love <<him>>|Gwylan Talk Clothes Valentines Love]]>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 5>><</link>><<ggyearning>>
	<br>
<</if>>

<</widget>>
